#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:26
msgid "Subtitle"
msgstr "Ondertitel"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:33
msgid ""
"The subtitling tool allows you to add and edit subtitles directly in the"
" timeline on a special subtitle track or by using the new subtitle"
" window. You can also import (SRT/ASS) and export (SRT) subtitles."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:36
msgid "There are 3 ways to add subtitle:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:39
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Menu**"
msgstr "Menu"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:42
msgid ":menuselection:`Project --> Subtitle --> Add Subtitle`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:45
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Keyboard**"
msgstr "Toetsenbord"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:48
msgid ":kbd:`Shift + S` adds a subtitle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:51
msgid "**Icon and Mouse**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:54
msgid ""
"Click the \"subtitle\" icon in the timeline toolbar to open the subtitle"
" track in the timeline."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:57
msgid "Double-click in the subtitle track to add a subtitle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:60
msgid "**Adding and editing text**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:63
msgid ""
"Add or editing text either directly into the subtitle clip or in the"
" subtitle window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:66
msgid "**Adjust the length of subtitle**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:69
msgid ""
"Grab the end of a subtitle with the mouse and lengthen or shorten it as"
" needed. Set subtitle in/out can be achieved with the same shortcut as to"
" set clip in/out (left/right parenthesis shortcut)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:73
msgid "**Subtitle window**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:79
msgid ""
"The subtitles window allows easier editing and also makes it possible to"
" easily navigate between subtitles with the left/right button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:82
msgid "With the plus sign, you can add subtitles."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:85
msgid ""
"The scissors are mostly here for divide subtitles: let's say your"
" subtitle text is too long and you want to make it 2 different subtitles."
" Put the cursor in the text widget where you want to cut and click the"
" scissors, it will split the text between 2 different subtitle items. The"
" scissors are only working when the playhead is over the subtitle itself."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:88
msgid "The tick adds the text to the subtitle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:91
msgid "**Import and export subtitle**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:94
msgid ""
"Importing SRT and ASS subtitle file: :menuselection:`Project -->"
" Subtitles --> Import subtitles file`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:97
msgid ""
"Exporting SRT subtitles only: :menuselection:`Project --> Subtitles -->"
" Export subtitles file`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:102
msgid ""
"SRT supports markup for: bold, italic, underline, text color and line"
" break."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:104
msgid "``<b>text in boldface</b>``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:105
msgid "``<i>text in italics</i>``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:106
msgid "``<u>text underlined</u>``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:107
msgid ""
"``<font color=\"#00ff00\"> text in green</font>`` you can use the font"
" tag only to change color."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:108
msgid ""
"And all combined: ``<font color=\"#00ff00\"><b><i><u>All combined</u></i"
"></b></font>``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:109
msgid ""
"**Line break:** Add on the end of each line a ``<br>`` (for break). Now"
" the srt file is stored correct and reopened with the line break. The"
" subtitle in the subtitle window will be all in 1 line after several save"
" but the breaks is working."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:111
msgid ":kbd:`Alt + arrow` jumps from subtitle to subtitle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:116
msgid "**Spelling check**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitle.rst:118
msgid ""
"Spelling check for subtitle is integrated and shows incorrect words by a"
" red wiggly line. Right-click on the word and you get a list of possible"
" words you can choose by click on it."
msgstr ""
